		"name": "Blog Application",
		"description": "This collection contains the RESTful APIs for a **Blog Application** built using **Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB**.\n\nThe application provides:\n\n- **User Management**: Registration, login, logout, authentication, and profile management.\n    \n- **Blog Management**: Create, read, update, and delete posts with ownership-based access control.\n    \n- **Engagement Features**: Like, comment, and save posts.\n    \n- **Security**: JWT authentication, role-based access control (RBAC), CORS, Helmet, and input validation.\n    \n- **Media Handling**: Image upload and storage with Cloudinary.\n    \n\n**Tech Stack**:\n\n- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js\n    \n- **Database**: MongoDB (local & Atlas)\n    \n- **Authentication**: JWT, bcrypt\n    \n- **File Storage**: Cloudinary\n    \n- **Security**: Helmet, CORS, Rate Limiting.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "41984587"
	},
